{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_017EeYU7srsaBxiHyiSeaPbc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. This is a Quarkus PetClinic application using:\n- Qute templates (Quarkus templating engine)\n- Panache (Quarkus ORM active record pattern)\n- JAX-RS (REST endpoints)\n- H2 for dev/test, PostgreSQL for prod\n\nThe migration to Spring Boot requires converting:\n- Qute templates → Thymeleaf templates\n- Panache entities → Spring Data JPA entities with repositories\n- JAX-RS resources → Spring MVC controllers\n- Quarkus DI → Spring DI\n- Quarkus i18n → Spring MessageSource\n\nLet me now execute the full migration:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1111,"cache_creation_input_tokens":564,"cache_read_input_tokens":63373,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":564,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":681},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d081c1a9-d8d9-4333-b4ac-461dffa2ff3d","uuid":"5c91c985-54ec-40dc-9f5b-568351e922d9"}
