{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0151JeQSzaBeNBGmth86i7K7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Mmo2zd1LaXYpY4qmh9MNpn","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/CHANGELOG.md","content":"# Migration Changelog: Quarkus to Spring Boot\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:35:00Z] [info] Project Analysis\n- Identified 27 Java source files in the Quarkus PetClinic application\n- Framework: Quarkus 3.30.5 with JAX-RS, Qute templates, Panache ORM, H2/PostgreSQL\n- Build system: Maven with Java 21\n- Detected Qute template engine with i18n message bundles (AppMessages, SpanishAppMessages)\n- Detected Panache active record pattern for entities (PanacheEntity)\n- Detected JAX-RS annotations for REST endpoints (@Path, @GET, @POST, etc.)\n- Static resources in `src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/` (Quarkus convention)\n- Templates in `src/main/resources/templates/` (Qute HTML files)\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:36:00Z] [info] Smoke Test Generation\n- Created `smoke.py` with 13 HTTP-based smoke tests covering:\n  - Welcome page (GET /)\n  - Find Owners page (GET /owners/find)\n  - List All Owners (GET /owners?lastName=)\n  - View specific owner (GET /owners/1001)\n  - New Owner form (GET /owners/new)\n  - Vets HTML page (GET /vets.html)\n  - Vets JSON API (GET /vets)\n  - Owners API list (GET /owners/api/list)\n  - New Pet form (GET /owners/1001/pets/new)\n  - New Visit form (GET /owners/1001/pets/1001/visits/new)\n  - Error page (GET /oups)\n  - Create Owner POST (POST /owners/new)\n  - Find Owner by last name (GET /owners?lastName=Davis)\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:37:00Z] [info] Dependency Migration (pom.xml)\n- Replaced Quarkus BOM and all Quarkus dependencies with Spring Boot 3.2.5 parent POM\n- Replaced `quarkus-rest` -> `spring-boot-starter-web`\n- Replaced `quarkus-rest-qute` -> `spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf`\n- Replaced `quarkus-hibernate-orm-panache` -> `spring-boot-starter-data-jpa`\n- Replaced `quarkus-hibernate-validator` -> `spring-boot-starter-validation`\n- Replaced `quarkus-jdbc-h2` -> `h2` (runtime scope)\n- Replaced `quarkus-jdbc-postgresql` -> `postgresql` (runtime scope)\n- Added `webjars-locator-core` for webjar URL resolution\n- Replaced `quarkus-junit5` + `rest-assured` -> `spring-boot-starter-test`\n- Replaced `quarkus-maven-plugin` -> `spring-boot-maven-plugin`\n- Removed: `quarkus-container-image-jib`, `quarkus-kubernetes`, `quarkus-web-dependency-locator`\n- Removed: native build profile, CSS SCSS compilation profile\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:38:00Z] [info] Configuration Migration\n- Converted `application.properties` from Quarkus profile syntax (%dev, %test, %prod) to Spring Boot\n- Changed datasource config: `quarkus.datasource.*` -> `spring.datasource.*`\n- Changed JPA config: `quarkus.hibernate-orm.*` -> `spring.jpa.*`\n- Set `spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=none` (using explicit schema.sql)\n- Created `schema.sql` with explicit table definitions matching the entity model\n- Renamed `import.sql` usage to `data.sql` (Spring Boot convention) via `spring.sql.init.data-locations`\n- Added `spring.sql.init.schema-locations=classpath:schema.sql`\n- Set `spring.jpa.defer-datasource-initialization=true` for proper initialization order\n- Added Thymeleaf configuration: `spring.thymeleaf.cache=false`\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:38:30Z] [info] Schema SQL Creation\n- Created `schema.sql` with all table definitions using `GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY` for all primary keys\n- This allows both explicit ID inserts (from data.sql seed data) and auto-generated IDs (from application)\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:39:00Z] [info] Package Restructuring\n- Changed base package from `org.quarkus.samples.petclinic` to `org.springframework.samples.petclinic`\n- Packages: model, owner, vet, visit, system\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:39:30Z] [info] Entity Migration\n- **Person (MappedSuperclass):**\n  - Removed `extends PanacheEntity`, added explicit `@Id` with `@GeneratedValue(strategy=IDENTITY)`\n  - Replaced `@FormParam` with standard getter/setters\n  - Changed from public fields to private fields with getters/setters (Spring convention)\n- **Owner:**\n  - Removed `extends PanacheEntity` (now inherits from Person)\n  - Removed `@FormParam` annotations, added getters/setters\n  - Removed Panache static methods (`findByLastName`, `listAll`, `persist`, `findById`, `attach`)\n  - Removed `getEntityManager().merge()` call\n- **Pet:**\n  - Removed `extends PanacheEntity`, added explicit `@Id` + `@GeneratedValue`\n  - Added getters/setters for all fields\n  - Added `getFormattedBirthDate()` helper for template display\n  - Removed `getEntityManager().merge()` call\n- **PetType:**\n  - Removed `extends PanacheEntity`, added explicit `@Id` + `@GeneratedValue`\n  - Removed Panache static `parse()` method (moved to PetTypeRepository.findByName)\n  - Removed Qute `@TemplateExtension` Formatter class\n- **Visit:**\n  - Removed `extends PanacheEntity`, added explicit `@Id` + `@GeneratedValue`\n  - Removed `@FormParam` annotations\n  - Removed Panache static `findByPetId()` (moved to VisitRepository)\n  - Added `getFormattedDate()` helper\n- **Vet:**\n  - Inherits from Person (preserved)\n  - Changed public fields to private with getters/setters\n- **Specialty:**\n  - Removed `extends PanacheEntity`, added explicit `@Id` + `@GeneratedValue`\n  - Changed public fields to private with getters/setters\n- **Vets:**\n  - Unchanged (already a plain DTO)\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:40:00Z] [info] Repository Creation (Spring Data JPA)\n- Created `OwnerRepository extends JpaRepository<Owner, Long>` with `findByLastName(String)`\n- Created `PetRepository extends JpaRepository<Pet, Long>`\n- Created `PetTypeRepository extends JpaRepository<PetType, Long>` with `findByName(String)`\n- Created `VisitRepository extends JpaRepository<Visit, Long>` with `findByPetId(Long)`\n- Created `VetRepository extends JpaRepository<Vet, Long>`\n- Created `SpecialtyRepository extends JpaRepository<Specialty, Long>`\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:41:00Z] [info] Controller Migration (JAX-RS -> Spring MVC)\n- **WelcomeController:** Replaced `@Path(\"/\")` + `@GET` + Qute TemplateInstance -> `@GetMapping(\"/\")` returning view name\n- **OwnerController:**\n  - Replaced `@Path(\"/owners\")` class annotation with individual `@GetMapping`/`@PostMapping` per method\n  - Replaced `@Inject Validator` + manual validation with `@Valid` + `BindingResult`\n  - Replaced Panache `Owner.findById()` / `Owner.listAll()` with `ownerRepository.findById()` / `findAll()`\n  - Replaced `owner.persist()` with `ownerRepository.save(owner)`\n  - Replaced `owner.attach()` with `ownerRepository.save(owner)`\n  - Replaced `@BeanParam Owner` with `@Valid Owner` (Spring form binding)\n  - Added `@ResponseBody` for JSON API endpoint\n- **PetController:**\n  - Replaced `@FormParam` with `@RequestParam`\n  - Replaced `PetType.parse(type)` with `petTypeRepository.findByName(typeName)`\n  - Replaced `pet.persist()` with `petRepository.save(pet)`\n- **VisitController:**\n  - Replaced `@BeanParam Visit` with `@RequestParam` parameters\n  - Replaced `visit.persist()` with `visitRepository.save(visit)`\n- **VetController:**\n  - Replaced `Vet.listAll()` with `vetRepository.findAll()`\n  - Added `@ResponseBody` for JSON endpoint\n- **CrashController:** Direct translation, `@Path(\"/oups\")` -> `@GetMapping(\"/oups\")`\n- **ErrorHandlerController:** Replaced `@ServerExceptionMapper` with `@ControllerAdvice` + `@ExceptionHandler`\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:42:00Z] [info] Removed Files\n- `JaxRsApplication.java` - Quarkus JAX-RS Application class (not needed in Spring Boot)\n- `Temporals.java` - Qute `@TemplateExtension` for date formatting (replaced with entity methods)\n- `Templates.java` - Qute `@CheckedTemplate` native method declarations\n- `TemplatesLocale.java` - Qute template locale wrapper\n- `AppMessages.java` - Qute `@MessageBundle` i18n interface\n- `SpanishAppMessages.java` - Qute `@Localized(\"es\")` i18n interface\n- `LocaleVariantCreator.java` - Qute Variant locale helper\n- `ErrorExceptionMapper.java` - Quarkus `@ServerExceptionMapper`\n- `OwnerForm.java` - JAX-RS `@FormParam` DTO (not needed with Spring form binding)\n- `LocalDateConverter.java` - JAX-RS `ParamConverter<LocalDate>` (Spring handles this natively)\n- `LocalDateParamConverterProvider.java` - JAX-RS `ParamConverterProvider`\n- `VisitComparator.java` - Replaced with lambda in Pet.getSortedVisits()\n- `SpecialityComparator.java` - Replaced with lambda in Vet.getSpecialties()\n- `src/main/docker/Dockerfile.native` - Quarkus native build Dockerfile\n- `src/main/docker/Dockerfile.jvm` - Quarkus JVM Dockerfile\n- `src/main/docker/Dockerfile.fast-jar` - Quarkus fast-jar Dockerfile\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:43:00Z] [info] Template Migration (Qute -> Thymeleaf)\n- Created `fragments/layout.html` as Thymeleaf fragment for header/navigation/scripts\n- Converted 9 templates from Qute syntax to Thymeleaf:\n  - `{#include base}` -> `th:replace=\"~{fragments/layout :: ...}\"`\n  - `{#insert body}...{/}` -> standard HTML structure with fragment includes\n  - `{#for item in list}...{/for}` -> `th:each=\"item : ${list}\"`\n  - `{#if condition}...{/if}` -> `th:if=\"${condition}\"`\n  - `{owner.firstName}` -> `th:text=\"${owner.firstName}\"`\n  - `{msg:key}` (i18n) -> hardcoded English strings (i18n simplified)\n  - `{pet.birthDate.format()}` (Qute extension) -> `th:text=\"${pet.formattedBirthDate}\"`\n  - `{pet.type.stringify}` (Qute extension) -> `th:text=\"${pet.type.name}\"`\n  - `{value ?: ''}` (Qute null-safe) -> `th:value=\"${value != null ? value : ''}\"`\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:43:30Z] [info] Static Resource Migration\n- Moved fonts from `META-INF/resources/fonts/` -> `static/fonts/`\n- Moved images from `META-INF/resources/images/` -> `static/images/`\n- Created `static/css/petclinic.css` by manually converting SCSS sources to plain CSS\n- Webjars served via Spring Boot's built-in webjar support + webjars-locator-core\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:44:00Z] [info] Dockerfile Migration\n- Replaced `mvn clean install -DskipTests -Dquarkus.profile=dev` with `mvn clean package -DskipTests`\n- Replaced `java -Dquarkus.profile=dev -jar target/quarkus-app/quarkus-run.jar` with `java -jar target/spring-petclinic-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT.jar`\n- Added `requests` Python package for smoke tests\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:44:30Z] [error] Data Loading Failure (First Attempt)\n- Error: `ScriptStatementFailedException: PRIMARY KEY ON PUBLIC.VETS(ID)` - duplicate key violation\n- Root Cause: `hibernate.ddl-auto=create-drop` created tables with auto-increment IDENTITY columns, conflicting with explicit ID values in data.sql\n- Resolution: Changed to `hibernate.ddl-auto=none` + explicit `schema.sql` with `GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY` for all tables\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:46:00Z] [info] Build Success (Second Attempt)\n- Docker image built successfully with Spring Boot 3.2.5\n- Application starts in ~8 seconds on port 8080\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:47:00Z] [info] Smoke Tests Passed\n- All 13/13 smoke tests passed\n- Welcome page, Owner CRUD, Pet forms, Visit forms, Vet list, JSON APIs, Error page all functional\n- Application running on dynamically assigned Docker port\n\n## [2026-03-14T10:48:00Z] [info] Migration Complete\n- Framework: Quarkus 3.30.5 -> Spring Boot 3.2.5\n- All business logic preserved\n- All endpoints functional\n- All seed data loaded correctly\n- Application builds, runs, and passes all tests\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":439,"cache_read_input_tokens":150891,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":439,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3773},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d081c1a9-d8d9-4333-b4ac-461dffa2ff3d","uuid":"5193c3d8-9e05-4bdd-a5ff-7d1cd61b319c"}
